    "description": "与Weyrdlets一起踏上暖心的旅程，在生产力中增添欢愉时光。 一起加入我们以社群为主轴的宠物模拟器并收养可爱的Weyrdlets。 在工作或玩游戏的同时让你和Weyrdlets的互动、打扮和玩耍为你带来更愉悦的体验～<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/3e591251412c0ba80503708cce2945dc.poster.avif?t=1770122358\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/3e591251412c0ba80503708cce2945dc.webm?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/3e591251412c0ba80503708cce2945dc.mp4?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >带欢乐回家就那么简单： 与你的虚拟宠物共度快乐时光，一起玩耍！</h2><br>体验领养一个拥有奇特能力的独特虚拟宠物。 就像在现实中一样，和你的宠物互动 – 摸摸、抓抓和喂食可爱的Weyrdlets。 在进行其他游戏的时候或是桌面上都可以喔！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/9bc439140c11f4480c9bee580922a9d1.poster.avif?t=1770122358\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/9bc439140c11f4480c9bee580922a9d1.webm?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/9bc439140c11f4480c9bee580922a9d1.mp4?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >让可爱的宠物陪伴你工作：住在桌面上的Weyrdlets！</h2><br>把工作也变成嬉戏！ 带虚拟宠物到电脑桌面陪你，不论是读书、看Netflix或是狂刷短影音，一起看影片、发呆和减压。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/7ae758ebaa0be638522c7bbf10fb4f04.poster.avif?t=1770122358\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/7ae758ebaa0be638522c7bbf10fb4f04.webm?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/7ae758ebaa0be638522c7bbf10fb4f04.mp4?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >客制化你的宠物，妆点可爱的它！</h2><br>帮它戴上千变万化的饰品和贴纸，养出专属于你的虚拟宠物。 不论是维京小帽到其他可爱的装饰，应有尽有。 透过打扮Weyrdlets与它的家，大胆地挥洒创意和展现你独特的风格吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/dd74b7b90cb6a8838c11d0035e0bb2a9.poster.avif?t=1770122358\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/dd74b7b90cb6a8838c11d0035e0bb2a9.webm?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/dd74b7b90cb6a8838c11d0035e0bb2a9.mp4?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >让虚拟宠物在电脑桌面上帮你提升生产力，拥有虚拟伙伴更是你的超能力！</h2><br>Weyrdlets不只会玩耍，还能帮你专注。 透过游戏内建的番茄时钟、待办事项和通知系统，提升你的生产力。 在宠物的陪伴中更专注和有效率。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/965be01c4e29b50829860812b03f464b.poster.avif?t=1770122358\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/965be01c4e29b50829860812b03f464b.webm?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366060/extras/965be01c4e29b50829860812b03f464b.mp4?t=1770122358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
